    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in mint condition. The interior shows no meaningful wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and all surfaces are clean and undamaged. Controls and displays function properly with no issues. Exterior is free of scratches, dents, or paint defects. Mechanically sound with no known issues.",
      "price": 46000.0,
